<RECORDNO>974782481</RECORDNO>
<TEXT>
--A fishing boat was towed to safety yesterday after taking on water off
Berwick. The Clyde-based Corsair was being towed to Seahouses for repairs when
a helicopter crew was summoned to lower pumping gear, which later failed.
Berwick lifeboat towed the Corsair back to Berwick.
